# ESP32-Smart-Environmental-Alert-Node 

A standalone IoT system that measures environmental data (temperature & humidity) and displays it live on an OLED screen and in a web browser вЂ” without internet or external cloud services. When temperature reaches or exceeds 28В°C, it automatically triggers a local alert: an LED turns on, the OLED shows вЂњWarm!вЂќ, and the web page highlights the value in red. Perfect for beginners who want to visualize sensor data locally over Wi-Fi while learning how IoT devices can actвЂ”not just observe.

